text: Öjeby IF is a sports club in Öjebyn in the town of Piteå in Sweden. It was established on 2 November 1922. The women's soccer team played in the Swedish top division in 1978. ==References== ==Other websites== *Official website Category:1922 establishments in Sweden Category:Handball clubs in Sweden Category:Swedish football clubs Category:Ice hockey teams in Sweden Category:Ski clubs in Sweden
